---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Karthik">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-20 relative">
    
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-accent-secondary/10 blur-[100px] rounded-full -z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>

    <section class="mb-20">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-white">Beyond the <span class="text-accent-primary">Terminal</span></h1>
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg text-slate-400">
        <p>
          I'm a Mobile & Systems Engineer who loves peeling back the layers of abstraction. Whether it's building React Native wrappers for Dart plugins or automating pipelines with GitLab CI, I focus on shipping robust, scalable mobile infrastructure.
        </p>
        <p>
          Currently, I'm driving mobile solutions at <strong>Irdeto</strong>, bridging the gap between high-level UI and low-level secure architectures.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="text-accent-primary">#</span> Work Experience
      </h2>
      
      <div class="border-l border-astro-700 ml-3 space-y-12">
        
        <div class="relative pl-8">
          <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-accent-primary shadow-[0_0_10px_#FF5D01]"></div>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">Mobile Application Developer</h3>
          <div class="mt-1 mb-3">
            <span class="text-slate-400 font-bold text-lg">Irdeto</span>
            <span class="block text-sm font-mono text-slate-500">Sep 2023 - Present ‚Ä¢ Pontiac, MI</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-400">
            Spearheading cross-platform secure solutions for the automotive industry.
            <br>‚Ä¢ <strong>Keystone SDK:</strong> Architected the React Native wrapper around Dart/Flutter plugins.
            <br>‚Ä¢ <strong>DevOps:</strong> Designed the complete mobile build & release pipeline using GitLab CI.
            <br>‚Ä¢ <strong>Architecture:</strong> Shaped mobile architecture through strict code reviews and secure coding standards.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative pl-8">
          <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-accent-secondary"></div>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">Full Stack Developer (Volunteer)</h3>
          <div class="mt-1 mb-3">
            <span class="text-slate-400 font-bold text-lg">ScoutBetter</span>
            <span class="block text-sm font-mono text-slate-500">May 2023 - Aug 2024</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-400">
            Contributed part-time to an end-to-end talent scouting platform. Built web and mobile interfaces to streamline the scouting process for athletes and recruiters.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative pl-8">
          <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-astro-600"></div>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">Graduate Teaching Assistant</h3>
          <div class="mt-1 mb-3">
            <span class="text-slate-400 font-bold text-lg">Central Michigan University</span>
            <span class="block text-sm font-mono text-slate-500">Jan 2023 - May 2023</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-400">
            Mentored undergraduate students in Computer Science fundamentals, graded assignments, and facilitated lab sessions to reinforce core programming concepts.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative pl-8">
          <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-astro-700"></div>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">Software Engineer</h3>
          <div class="mt-1 mb-3">
            <span class="text-slate-400 font-bold text-lg">WieLabs</span>
            <span class="block text-sm font-mono text-slate-500">Dec 2019 - Nov 2021 ‚Ä¢ Hyderabad, India</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">
            Delivered 7+ full-stack mobile applications, handling everything from Native Android/Flutter UI to Python/Node backends.
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
            <div class="bg-astro-800/50 p-3 rounded border border-astro-700">
                <strong class="text-white block">Hing & Carnival</strong>
                <span class="text-slate-400">Social/Event apps (Flutter + Flask). Implemented HLS streaming via FFMPEG.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-astro-800/50 p-3 rounded border border-astro-700">
                <strong class="text-white block">Loudcar</strong>
                <span class="text-slate-400">IoT Controller app using Bluetooth Classic for LED displays.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-astro-800/50 p-3 rounded border border-astro-700">
                <strong class="text-white block">Witness & Trendition</strong>
                <span class="text-slate-400">Native Android (Kotlin) apps for News & Retail management.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-astro-800/50 p-3 rounded border border-astro-700">
                <strong class="text-white block">Clock365</strong>
                <span class="text-slate-400">Attendance system with Barcode scanners (FastAPI backend).</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="text-accent-secondary">#</span> Education
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-astro-800/30 border border-astro-700 flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">MS in Computer Science</h3>
                <span class="text-accent-secondary font-mono text-sm">Central Michigan University</span>
                <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400 text-sm">
                    Specialized in Advanced Algorithms and Systems.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-astro-700/50 flex justify-between items-center">
                <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">2022 - 2024</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-accent-secondary/10 text-accent-secondary text-xs font-bold">GPA: 3.9/4.0</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-astro-800/30 border border-astro-700 flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">B.Tech in Computer Science</h3>
                <span class="text-accent-secondary font-mono text-sm">BV Raju Institute (BVRIT)</span>
                <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400 text-sm">
                   Core Computer Science curriculum with a focus on Software Engineering.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-astro-700/50 flex justify-between items-center">
                <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">2018 - 2022</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-accent-secondary/10 text-accent-secondary text-xs font-bold">GPA: 9.7/10</span>
            </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="text-slate-500">#</span> AFK (Away From Keyboard)
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-astro-800/50 border border-astro-700 hover:border-accent-primary/50 transition-colors">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">üì≤</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Android Rom Modder</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">
            I don't just use phones; I root them. Experienced with <strong>LineageOS, Magisk, and Fastboot</strong>. I enjoy flashing custom kernels and optimizing the Android runtime for peak performance.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-astro-800/50 border border-astro-700 hover:border-accent-primary/50 transition-colors">
           <div class="text-3xl mb-4">üèãÔ∏è</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Fitness & Discipline</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">
            Consistency in the gym mirrors consistency in code. Whether it's debugging a race condition or hitting a PR, the process is the same: progressive overload and discipline.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>